headline: Verisk (VRSK): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q4 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, Verisk has been a great trade. While the S&P 500 was flat, the stock price has climbed by 10.3% to $291.53 per share. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
